        "text": "Subjects with MET alterations, namely: METex14 skipping alterations in plasma and/or tissue, as determined by the central laboratory or by an assay with appropriate regulatory status will, be enrolled into the trial. For these subjects, sufficient tumor tissue and/or plasma is requested to allow additional testing; MET amplification only in plasma defined by a positive LBx test, as determined by the central laboratory or by an assay with appropriate regulatory status; Based on the outcome of the interim analysis in 12 LBx selected subjects: MET amplification only in tissue defined by a positive TBx with a gain of at least 4 copies of the MET gene, as determined by the central laboratory or by an assay with appropriate regulatory status.",
